  "title": "*URGENT* Temp Patient Service Associate (Training Provided!!) #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         \nProviding frontline\ncustomer service and handling of any registrations, and appointments</p><p>-         \nWorking\nclosely with the practitioners and nurses to provide excellent patient care</p><p>-         \nProvide chaperone assistance to\ndoctors/nurses</p><p>-         \nAttend to any requests, emails and phone\nenquiries</p><p>-         \nCollection\nof payments and basic admin duties</p><p>-         \nAd-hoc\nduties</p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>-         \nMinimum\nN/O/A Levels or Diploma in any studies are encouraged to apply</p><p>-         \nAble to\ncommit a minimum of 3 months</p><p>-         \nWilling\nto walk and stand for long hours</p><p>-         \nExperience\nin customer service preferred but not a must as training will be provided</p><p>-         \nOffice\nhours, 5.5 days</p><p>-         \nAble\nto start immediately/on short notice</p><p>All qualified\napplicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />\nRecruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.\n199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
